==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Suppliance
<hw>Sup*pli"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Supply</er>.]</ety> <def>That which supplies a want; assistance; a
gratification; satisfaction.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The perfume and <qex>suppliance</qex> of a minute.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suppliance</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Suppliance
<hw>Sup*pli"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Suppliant</er>.]</ety> <def>Supplication; entreaty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When Greece her knee in <qex>suppliance</qex> bent.</q>
<rj><qau>Halleck.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suppliant</ent>⟦br⟧
